{"title_page": "1987 in heavy metal music", "text_new": "{{Year in music|1987}}\n{{Year nav topic5|1987|heavy metal music}}\n{{unreferenced|date=October 2016}}\nThis is a timeline documenting the events of [[Heavy Metal music|heavy metal]] in the year 1987.\n\n==Newly formed bands==\n*[[Alchemist (band)|Alchemist]] \n*[[Alice in Chains]]\n* [[Asphyx]]\n* [[Autopsy (band)|Autopsy]]\n*[[Cynic (band)|Cynic]]\n*[[Danzig (band)|Danzig]]\n*[[Deicide (band)|Deicide]]\n*[[Disharmonic Orchestra]]\n*[[Entombed (band)|Entombed]]\n*[[Follow for Now]]\n*[[Herm\u00e9tica]]\n*[[Hobbs' Angel of Death]]\n*[[Impellitteri]]\n*[[Intruder (American band)|Intruder]]\n*[[Malevolent Creation]]\n*[[Meliah Rage]]\n* [[Meshuggah]]\n*[[Mortification (band)|Mortification]]\n* [[Nirvana (band)|Nirvana]]\n*[[Nocturnus]]\n* [[Phantom Blue]]\n* [[Pink Cream 69]]\n* [[Primordial (band)|Primordial]]\n*[[Ripping Corpse]]\n* [[Rollins Band]]\n*[[Rotting Christ]]\n*[[Samael (band)|Samael]] \n* [[Therion (band)|Therion]]\n*[[Tiamat (band)|Tiamat]] \n*[[Transmetal (band)|Transmetal]] \n* [[U.D.O.]]\n*[[Von (band)|Von]] \n* [[Winger (band)|Winger]]\n\n==Albums & EPs==\n{{Div col|colwidth=20em}}\n* ADX \u2013 ''Suprematie''\n* [[Aerosmith]] - ''[[Permanent Vacation (album)|Permanent Vacation]]''\n* [[Agent Steel]] - ''[[Unstoppable Force]]'' \n* Agentz \u2013 ''Stick To Your Guns''\n* Alias (US) \u2013 ''Alias''\n* [[Alice Cooper]] - ''[[Raise Your Fist and Yell]]''\n* [[The Angels (Australian band)|The Angels]], aka Angel City \u2013 ''[[Live Line]]'' (live)\n* [[Anthem (band)|Anthem]] - ''Bound to Break''\n* [[Anthrax (American band)|Anthrax]] - ''[[Among the Living]]''\n* Anthrax - ''[[I'm the Man (EP)|I'm the Man]]'' (EP)\n* [[Anvil (band)|Anvil]] - ''[[Strength of Steel]]''\n* Apocrypha - ''The Forgotten Scroll''\n* [[Armored Saint]] - ''[[Raising Fear]]''\n* [[Atomkraft]] \u2013 ''Conductors of Noize'' (EP)\n* [[Autograph (American band)|Autograph]] - ''[[Loud and Clear (Autograph album)|Loud and Clea